<view class="page-shell">
  <view class="section-card feedback-hero">
    <view class="section-kicker">问题反馈</view>
    <view class="section-title">哪里不顺手，直接告诉我们</view>
    <view class="section-desc">显示错位、发布失败、想加功能都可以写在这里。我们会把反馈保存下来，后面集中优化。</view>
  </view>

  <view class="section-card">
    <view class="field-label">反馈类型</view>
    <picker range="{{typeOptions}}" value="{{typeIndex}}" bindchange="onTypeChange">
      <view class="field-picker">{{typeOptions[typeIndex]}}</view>
    </picker>

    <view class="divider"></view>

    <view class="field-label">具体问题</view>
    <textarea
      class="feedback-textarea"
      maxlength="300"
      value="{{form.content}}"
      placeholder="比如：发布页联系电话输入框文字被挡住；或者希望增加某个搭子类型..."
      bindinput="onContentInput"
    />
    <view class="textarea-count">{{contentLength}} / 300</view>

    <view class="divider"></view>

    <view class="field-label">联系方式（选填）</view>
    <input
      class="field-input"
      maxlength="60"
      value="{{form.contact}}"
      placeholder="微信、电话或邮箱都可以，方便我们追问细节"
      bindinput="onContactInput"
    />
  </view>

  <view class="section-card tip-card">
    <view class="tip-title">反馈小提示</view>
    <view class="tip-line">如果是页面错位，可以写清楚在哪个页面、点了什么之后出现。</view>
    <view class="tip-line">如果是发布或加入失败，把提示文字也一起写上，排查会快很多。</view>
  </view>

  <button class="primary-btn submit-btn" bindtap="submitFeedback" loading="{{submitting}}">
    提交反馈
  </button>
</view>
